    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Remove the intermediate shaft assembly (A)."
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "To prevent damage to the transfer oil seal (B), the intermediate shaft must be pulled out horizontally."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
